data.description: This well-maintained home in the coveted Carleton Falls Subdivision offers a blend of comfort and convenience. Featuring durable vinyl plank flooring and carpeted bedrooms, the residence boasts a kitchen adorned with granite countertops. Throughout the house, ceiling fans provide comfort, while the primary bedroom enjoys a vaulted ceiling. Its strategic location places it within minutes of Ft. Eustis, Naval Weapons Station Yorktown, and Oakland Industrial Park. With multiple access points to I-64 and other key Peninsula roads, this property offers both accessibility and comfort. VA Assumable loan can be transfer to a qualified veteran that can also transfer the eligibility onto their own VA eligibility.
